sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor PM as PMS 提资平台
  participant PA as platform_api<br/>(embed_url / workflow_sync / delete / cache_preload)
  participant RA as review_api.rs<br/>(sync_review_form_with_task_status)
  participant Frontend as plant3d-web<br/>(iframe embed)
  participant DB as SurrealDB

  Note over PM,PA: 1) 入口: 生成嵌入校审 URL
  PM->>PA: POST /api/review/embed-url<br/>{project_id, user_id, form_id?, role}
  PA->>PA: create_token(JWT, exp, role, workflow_mode)
  PA-->>PM: { url, token, relative_path, query{form_id} }
  PM->>Frontend: iframe src = ${url}?user_token=...&form_id=...

  Note over PM,PA: 2) PMS 驱动工作流 (无需人工操作 UI)
  PM->>PA: POST /api/review/workflow/sync<br/>{form_id, token(S2S), action: active/agree/return, actor}
  PA->>PA: verify_s2s_token
  alt action=query
    PA->>DB: 聚合查询 (records + comments + attachments + form 状态)
    PA-->>PM: SyncWorkflowResponse<br/>{title, models, taskId, records,<br/>annotationComments, attachments, currentNode, taskStatus}
  else action=active/agree/return
    PA->>DB: 更新 review_forms 状态<br/>(归并到 review_tasks workflow)
    PA->>RA: sync_review_form_with_task_status<br/>(写回 review_forms)
    PA-->>PM: next_step 或错误
  end

  Note over PM,PA: 3) 预热缓存 (待进入时)
  PM->>PA: POST /api/review/cache/preload<br/>{project_id, initiator}
  PA-->>PM: task_id 返回

  Note over PM,PA: 4) 删除/清理
  PM->>PA: POST /api/review/delete<br/>(按 form_id 软删)
  PA->>RA: mark_review_form_deleted
  PA->>DB: UPDATE review_forms/tasks SET deleted=true
